03:50.830 --> 03:51.854
MORNING !

03:51.860 --> 03:53.589
GOD, YOU SCARED ME.

03:53.600 --> 03:55.329
YOU'RE UP EARLY.

03:55.330 --> 03:58.151
YOU SLEPT
LIKE A FUCKING BABY.

03:58.160 --> 03:59.855
