04:14.500 --> 04:16.058
WOW, THIS IS
KINDA RACY.

04:16.060 --> 04:17.948
HEY, HEY, NO !

04:18.960 --> 04:20.393
IS THAT YOUR NOVEL ?

04:20.400 --> 04:21.890
