WHAT IT IS YET.

04:21.900 --> 04:23.720
WHEN DO I
GET TO READ IT ?

04:23.730 --> 04:24.992
WHEN IT'S READY.

04:25.000 --> 04:26.353
IF IT'S EVER READY.

04:26.360 --> 04:27.850
WELL, NOW WHO'S
"CHRISTINA"

04:27.860 --> 04:29.794
IS THAT LIKE
YOUR FICTIONAL ALTER-EGO ?

04:29.800 --> 04:30.824
YOUR HOLDEN CAULFIELD ?

04:30.830 --> 04:34.596
SHE'S MORE LIKE
MY HUMBERT HUMBERT.

04:36.230 --> 04:39.620
MY CONSTANCE CHA'I'I'ERLY ?

04:41.100 --> 04:43.557
SHE'S LIKE HERMIONE
IN THE HARRY POTTER BOOKS.

04:43.560 --> 04:45.027
WHAT WOULD
YOU RATHER HAVE,

04:45.030 --> 04:47.658
SOME OVERLY EDUCATED
GASBAG LIKE TREVOR ?

04:47.660 --> 04:50.299
OR A SEMI-LITERATE
FUCK MACHINE LIKE ME, C'MON ?

04:50.300 --> 04:51.790
THAT'S A NO-BRAINER.

04:51.800 --> 04:53.199
NO PUN INTENDED.

04:53.200 --> 04:57.057
HEY, I HAVE
SOMETHING FOR YOU.

05:01.860 --> 05:04.055
I KNOW IT'S SMALL,
BUT IT IS A DIAMOND.

05:04.060 --> 05:05.994
YOU THINK I CARE
ABOUT DIAMONDS ?

05:06.000 --> 05:09.026
WILL YOU MARRY ME,
BRENDA CHENOWITH ?

05:09.030 --> 05:11.828
